  "description": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(194, 79, 74);\">The carriers that support self-pickup with official logistics waybills are: USPS, FedEx, UPS.<br/><br/>&nbsp;official logistics waybill: generating a USPS waybill is charged according to the labeled price, while generating UPS or FedEx requires an additional $2.</span><br/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/0a8c3fb5-fb55-4de7-9cc0-19cf7e0fc783.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/41f87ede-953c-4ac2-9da2-eb279730e2f9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/a056b91c-92db-44f0-945e-143d833c92a0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/b2096429-303e-404e-8a44-fe77260df714.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/b0462b9b-b3dd-4dd7-9a4f-173d307c9cd3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/6ecd1c5b-3c18-460e-9d64-097d6977f71d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/></p>",
